dc_description_s: Dr. Ludwig Reichert Verlag. Herausgegeben vom Sonderforschungsbereich 19 "Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients". Companion text: Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients / Herausgegeben vom Sonderforschungsbereich 19 der Universitat Tubinger. Wiesbaden : Dr. Ludwig Reichert Verlag, 1977- Issued in fascicles. Supplements and other related publications (Arbeitsheft and Beiheft). ISBN: 1882267402. North Decimal Degree 42.028611. South Decimal Degree 12.557778. East Decimal Degree 71.121944. West Decimal Degree 38.013611. Alternate title: Tourismus im Vorderen Orient = Tourism in the Middle East. Map is: fascicle TAVO A X 19 of "Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients : TAVO. Insets: [Cyprus] and [The Levant] (1:2,000,000). Ancillary map: Tourismus in der Turkei = Tourism in Turkey (1:4,000,000). ISBN: 3882267240. Includes graphs and outline map showing age of data used (1972-1982). Shows places with international tourism, pilgrimage sites and tourist facilities.
